Titolo: Abomination: The Nemesis Project

Anno: 1999

Descrizione: Abomination: The Nemesis Project, known in the United States as simply Abomination, is a real-time tactics/action video game released in 1999. In the game, the player leads a team of eight genetically altered supersoldiers (marines) to defeat an infestation of a global genetic plague which slowly turns into a superorganism.
Abomination was met with mixed reception, with the game's A.I. being the most primary of grievances.